<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.3.3">
<l>entam pirāṉā reḻiltiru mārvarkkuc</l>
<l>canta maḻakiya tāmarait tāḷarkku</l>
<l>vintiraṉ ṟāṉu meḻiluṭaik kiṇkiṇi</l>
<l>tantuva ṉāyniṉṟāṉ tālēlō tāmaraik kaṇṇaṉē tālēlō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Lord, Indra himself, having given the tinkling anklet</l>
<l>that possesses beauty for [your] beautiful lotus feet</l>
<l>[and] sandalwood for [your] beautiful, sacred chest,</l>
<l>he stands nearby, tālēlō! You with lotus eyes, tālēlō!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
